kings and all those in authority, that we may live peaceful and quiet lives in all godliness and holiness. This is good, and pleases God our Savior, who wants all men to be saved and to come to a knowledge of the truth. For there is one God and one mediator between God and men, the man Christ Jesus’</font>, <b>1TIMOTHY 2: 1-5</b><br><br>This verse showcase the need of all to be saved it is therefore not an option but the option of which without it there is no redemption or no Christianity. One cannot claim to be a believer of Christ if he/she does not obey his call over his/her life which is to follow in his footsteps by word and deed.</blockquote><br><br>I really like this part. Thanks again for your intelligent response.</span>
